---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---
<Base title="Home" description="Stem Cell — a resource model runtime for building APIs from YAML specs.">
  <main class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 py-24 text-center">
    <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-neutral-800 bg-neutral-900/60 px-4 py-1.5 text-xs font-medium text-neutral-400">
      <span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-green-400"></span>
      Open-source runtime
    </div>

    <h1 class="mt-8 text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight sm:text-6xl">
      <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-400 via-purple-400 to-pink-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">Stem Cell</span>
    </h1>

    <p class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-neutral-400">
      Define your data model in YAML. Get a full REST API, admin UI, auth, and
      migrations — instantly. One binary, zero boilerplate.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4 sm:flex-row">
      <a href="/admin" class="rounded-xl bg-indigo-600 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-lg shadow-indigo-600/20 transition hover:bg-indigo-500 hover:shadow-indigo-500/30">
        Admin Dashboard
      </a>
      <a href="/api/docs" class="rounded-xl border border-neutral-700 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-neutral-300 transition hover:border-neutral-500 hover:text-white">
        API Documentation
      </a>
    </div>

    <section class="mt-24 grid gap-8 text-left sm:grid-cols-3">
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-neutral-800 bg-neutral-900/40 p-6">
        <div class="mb-3 text-2xl">
          <svg class="h-7 w-7 text-indigo-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M19.5 14.25v-2.625a3.375 3.375 0 00-3.375-3.375h-1.5A1.125 1.125 0 0113.5 7.125v-1.5a3.375 3.375 0 00-3.375-3.375H8.25m2.25 0H5.625c-.621 0-1.125.504-1.125 1.125v17.25c0 .621.504 1.125 1.125 1.125h12.75c.621 0 1.125-.504 1.125-1.125V11.25a9 9 0 00-9-9z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-neutral-100">Spec-Driven</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-neutral-500">
          Author your resources, fields, and relations in a single YAML file.
          The runtime does the rest.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-neutral-800 bg-neutral-900/40 p-6">
        <div class="mb-3 text-2xl">
          <svg class="h-7 w-7 text-purple-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M5.25 14.25h13.5m-13.5 0a3 3 0 01-3-3m3 3a3 3 0 100 6h13.5a3 3 0 100-6m-16.5-3a3 3 0 013-3h13.5a3 3 0 013 3m-19.5 0a4.5 4.5 0 01.9-2.7L5.737 5.1a3.375 3.375 0 012.7-1.35h7.126c1.062 0 2.062.5 2.7 1.35l2.587 3.45a4.5 4.5 0 01.9 2.7m0 0a3 3 0 01-3 3m0 3h.008v.008h-.008v-.008zm0-6h.008v.008h-.008v-.008zm-3 6h.008v.008h-.008v-.008zm0-6h.008v.008h-.008v-.008z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-neutral-100">Single Binary</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-neutral-500">
          Compiled Rust runtime with built-in Postgres, auth, email, and a
          static admin frontend. Just add a database.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-neutral-800 bg-neutral-900/40 p-6">
        <div class="mb-3 text-2xl">
          <svg class="h-7 w-7 text-pink-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75m-3-7.036A11.959 11.959 0 013.598 6 11.99 11.99 0 003 9.749c0 5.592 3.824 10.29 9 11.623 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.31-.21-2.571-.598-3.751h-.152c-3.196 0-6.1-1.248-8.25-3.285z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-neutral-100">Auth Built-In</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-neutral-500">
          Email/password, magic links, and OAuth providers — configured in
          the same spec, protected by default.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Base>
